Package: Metrix
Type: Package
Title: This gives the metrics for a n*n confusion matrix
Version: 0.1.0
Author: R A @ NMIMS Hyd
Maintainer: https://github.com/R2AatNMIMS-H-2023
Description: This package is used to calculate the following Metrics for a n*n confusion MatriX
1. Sensitivity
2. Specificity
3. Accuracy
4. Precision
5. False Positive Rate (FPR)
6. False Negative Rate (FNR)
7. F1 Score
6. Balanced Classification Accuracy (BCA)
License: Free to use
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
